text:
RT @NYDailyNews: Dr. Thomas Freeman, an acclaimed professor and debate coach whose many students included Martin Luther King Jr., has died at 100.

King was a student at Morehouse College in Atlanta when he learned from Freeman, who was a visiting professor.
